#-------PUNTO 2-------
### Consultar usuarios:
GET http://localhost:3000/users?page=1&limit=3
x-auth: admin_auth

### Consultar usuarios sin admin_auth:
GET http://localhost:3000/users?page=1&limit=3
x-auth: Password2

#-------PUNTO 3-------
### Crear Usuario 1 (ID: 1):
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Usuario Uno",
    "email": "uno@prueba.com",
    "password": "Password1",
    "confirm_password": "Password1"
}

